            <p class = "about"> Akins Ballet Folklorico is a student led and student taught club at Akins High School.<br> 
                Student Rachel Rivera from the Class of 2018 founded the group when she was a <br>
                freshman in 2015 and became president of the club. Rachel Rivera is the "Maestra", <br> 
                teacher, of Akins Ballet Folklorico. She organizes, teaches, and coreographs all dances. 
            </p>
            <p class = "aboutContinued"> Akins Ballet Folklorico partners with the Latinos Unidos Club at Akins High <br>
                School to perform at Akins's Cinco De Mayo Show every year. We want to thank Latinos <br>
                Unidos for all the great opportunites they have given Akins Ballet Folklorico from the start. <br>
                For letting us unite as one culture at school.
            </p>
            
